message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as the paper deals with statistical voice conversion using spectral differentials. Other likely categories could be cs.SI (Speech Processing and Synthesis) as the paper deals with voice conversion, cs.SD.LG (Learning for Speech and Audio Processing) as the paper proposes a data-driven method for lifter training, cs.SD.AU (Audio and Speech Processing) as the paper deals with voice conversion and waveform modification, cs.CL (Computation and Language) as the paper proposes computationally efficient methods for voice conversion.
